vote.title: Authorize (1) an increase in the joint election agreement and election services contract between the City of Dallas and Dallas County for the May 3, 2025; and (2) an increase in appropriations in an amount not to exceed $109,367.00 in the City Secretary’s Office from General Fund Contingency Reserve - Not to exceed $109,366.44, from $1,033,010.75 to $1,142,377.19 - Financing: General Fund Contingency Reserve (see Fiscal Information)
